25</a><br />\n<br />\n而家王岐山根本就係做緊現實版既Frank Underwood，Frank Underwood做左副總統之後，又係主力對付中國問題，而家王岐山上任，佢又係比習總派去應對美國貿易戰問題<br />\n<br />\n而家係土共D人睇紙牌屋睇上腦，玩埋Cosplay Frank Underwood呀！？下一步係咪會王岐山整古習近平，搞到習近平無得做下台，最後王岐山坐正！？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b093aa5321463683c9a18313426c8c6b4ab5fb7","tid":598223,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T10:29:25.000Z","msg":"frank underwood 係gay<br />\n王歧山....?"},{"pid":"aa0bcca3dcd638acde756103f6f8b58637edf7a4","tid":598223,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T10:37:57.000Z","msg":"你睇上腦喳"},{"pid":"defc1665658250698258b63000ac88f62d0cac77","tid":598223,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b093aa5321463683c9a18313426c8c6b4ab5fb7","tid":598223,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T10:29:25.000Z","msg":"frank underwood 係gay<br />\n王歧山....?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T10:38:16.000Z","msg":"同李克強搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da5256893f2d5c9300444f638c495d6f18841995","tid":598223,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T10:39:54.000Z","msg":"咁Winnie 呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00fe92ee4e9d6d77a063cff0a358ab8e1a24941e","tid":598223,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T10:40:34.000Z","msg":"全中國風評就算係共黨內部<br />\n<br />\n對王歧山 能力 評價都遠勝於雜種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3739f7dfc78dee7396c2238230a1e4adcb960e5","tid":598223,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T10:41:34.000Z","msg":"記得好耐之前有新聞講 王岐山好撚中意睇hoc"},{"pid":"251fca0f52cc98e17e7cbb6b7bf668674b4fcc92","tid":598223,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00fe92ee